Text: Deals attached to basisThanks for all your help today I apologize for my propensity to catch you away from your desk We all have to be good at something right Anyway here are the fixedprice volumes associated with a portion of the basis transactions done in June and Q Im missing some deal numbers but Im guessing you wont need those Deal Number Month Date Volume Price June EUX June July EUP July August EUGL September QS September In other news a few of us including Art and I are getting together for drinks after work tomorrow if you or anyone else is interested Coincidentally the State Bar is the location of choice so I hope you arent State Bared out Let us know I believe everyone will be swinging by around or so Thanks again Charlie Sanchez Gelber Associates
